---
title: Quick Double Chermoula Lamb & Chickpea Rice Bowl with Baby Leaves & Yoghurt
description: Chermoula spice is the ultimate complimentary seasoning for tender lamb and protein-rich chickpeas, and with hearty rice
plus a cooling yoghurt, this bowl is a burst of flavour in every bite! We can't wait to dig in.

*We’ve replaced the couscous in this recipe with jasmine rice due
to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/666be5c6f6d6f122b49fdd92-7d1e3831.jpeg
